# model-inference backend: ephemeral sqlite + object-store + GGUF fixture
# installed on demand via
# demo/model-inference/backend-king-php/scripts/install-llama-runtime.sh.
demo/model-inference/backend-king-php/.local/

# Model weights MUST NEVER be checked in (they are large and provenance
# belongs on a model registry / object store, not in git). Catch-all
# patterns repo-wide — if you actually need a tiny test fixture that
# overlaps, negate it explicitly under the owning demo directory, not
# by weakening these rules.
*.gguf
*.safetensors
*.pt
*.pth
*.ckpt
*.onnx
*.tflite
*.bin
# Exception: cargo vendor + ring/flate2 test fixtures + quiche cmake
# artifacts need to keep their `.bin` names. These trees are already
# scoped by earlier ignore rules (target/, .cargo/) and are not
# shipped as part of any commit anyway.

**/CMakeFiles/
**/CMakeCache.txt
**/cmake-build-*/
**/cmake_install.cmake
**/compile_commands.json
__pycache__/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/

